{% if memverse_enabled == "true" %}
**Memverse Sync:** If the `--json` output contains a non-null `memverse_sync` field, execute the MCP call to persist this failure pattern to semantic memory:

```
CallMcpTool(
  server="user-Memverse",
  toolName="upsert_memory",
  arguments={
    "content": <memverse_sync.content>,
    "metadata": <memverse_sync.metadata>,
    "upsert_key": "signature",
    "domain": "{{ memverse_domain }}"
  }
)
```

This is best-effort — if the MCP call fails, log the error and continue.  The local JSONL record is the source of truth.
{% endif %}
